Bany: Aine, Astral, Daremyth.  Excellent game. Tower in treasure zone and gremlin dwelling allowed both to develop large gremlins stack. This was mostly native armies fight as banks were scarce and small. The connections, though, made up for it: most of the treasure zones were unavailable but towns were really close which allowed me to rush after taking 1-conservatory and 3 exp shop. The map offered almost no gems so we did not reach TP until end of game in 133
